    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="witness" subtype="poem" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" rhyme="aa">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l><handShift new="#HANDJR1833-34" script="cursive" medium="ink"/>oh softly blew the mo<subst><del>u</del><add rend="overwriting">r</add></subst>n<subst><del>t</del><add rend="overwriting">i</add></subst>ng breeze<ref type="gloss" target="oh_softly_blew_the_morning_breeze_poem_glosses_textual.php#MOUNTINGBREEZE"/><add rend="linenumber-right-JR">810</add></l>
                    <l>Through <placeName corresp="#CHIAVENNA">Chiavenna</placeName>s <name type="botanical" corresp="#MYRTLE">myrtle trees</name>,</l>
                <l>And oer the green hills viny spread</l>
                <l>That rose in many a rounded head</l>
                <l>Beneath the <geogName corresp="#ALPS">Alpine</geogName> rocks of red</l>
                    <l>And the fresh snow had fall&#x02BC;n that night<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">815</add></l> 
                <l>And sprinkled with its mantle white</l>
                <l>The mountain amphitheatre</l>
                    <l>That rose around us far and near<ref type="gloss" target="oh_softly_blew_the_morning_breeze_poem_glosses_contextual.php#MOUNTAINAMPHITHEATRE"/></l>
                <l>Though in such far confusion hurled</l>
                    <l>They looked to rule oer all the world<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">820</add></l> 
                <l>And the white clouds seemed to immerse,</l>
                <l>Another ruin'd universe.</l>
                </lg>
           </div>
